---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 103
Description: Japanese Ode
Format: verse
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Phantom Flux of Life
---
On Mount Yoshino each returning year.
How beautiful the cherries blossom gay.
Split the tree open wide and then draw near.
Tell me where is the flower now. I pray.
